data.title: Horrible bar service!
data.text: With only 6 people sitting around the bar with 2 bartenders.... I had to wait to get a drink and order food... Because the bartenders were too busy talking to each other, eating and on their phones! It makes sense why this place is dead! Great location, horrible everything else! I don't think one of the "bartender ever put her phone down! Will never return here! Oh, and for the female handicapped... Sorry your toilet seat is half broke off.. Ouch! ($10 fix)!

data.title: Big bar filled with coasties
data.text: Johnny O's has a reputation for being a hang out for coasties, frat boys and sorority girls. It is a nice bar in itself. It has several hoops for shooting basketballs, a big bar downstairs, a bar upstairs on the roof and a nice outdoor area. There's also a lot of seating and a big dance floor. Some nights it can be quite dead at Johnny O's but for most nights its a good back up bar to go to. For me personally, I get bored easily at Johnny O's because it attracts a homogeneous crowd...
